Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:04.87,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}As times change,\Ndifficult cases increase in number!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.87,0:00:06.77,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's case is a manhunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:08.77,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Don't put out the flames of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:10.64,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the truth in people's hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.64,0:00:13.14,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:15.47,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
