Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:47.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Noriko Okaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.32,0:01:50.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping you could find the address
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:54.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of a man named Tsuyoshi Kitagawa-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.06,0:01:58.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon my asking, but how are you two related?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:02:03.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I met him in early June, during a trip to Shinshu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:10.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think much of him at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:15.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but lately I've wanted to see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:21.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it! You've fallen in love with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:26.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:30.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Just a simple search. No need for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:32.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Here's some tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:34.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:37.43,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why's she so nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:40.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Do you have any clues or leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:44.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. His license plate number
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:46.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and a quick sketch of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:50.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! He's quite the unique individual!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:54.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:56.55,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This sketch...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:58.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Thank you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:07.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be a cinch! I can use his license plate number
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:10.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to get his address from the transportation office!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:16.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure she really likes him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:19.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:21.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that when you draw someone's picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:26.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,your feelings for that person go into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:29.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her drawing doesn't look very—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:30.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of your lip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:34.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go do your homework\Nand mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:36.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:37.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:41.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}. You shouldn't get in the way of—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:44.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko Okaya-{\i1}san{\i0}, lives at—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:46.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of his work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:48.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:50.83,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I already saw what I needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:55.28,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A handkerchief. Is it hers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:57.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'll be back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:03:59.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:10.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Let's see. 3-9-8... Sumire Lodge...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:12.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:16.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Thanks for bringing me my handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:18.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}. Want some cocoa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:19.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:26.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a nice apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:27.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what's your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:35.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to work at a business firm,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:36.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but now I'm taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:42.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got sick. I'm recuperating now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:47.76,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Kerosene?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.36,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:53.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I don't see any gas heaters...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.84,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A can of mace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:58.87,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Huh? What's that picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:02.78,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's dated May 19th...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:08.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Now, now. Is a girl's apartment that rare for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:13.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This was my boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:16.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,until he dumped me a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:20.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So now I'm looking for a new boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:27.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That man in the sketch sure seems different, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:33.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking things might go smoother with a different type of person!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:37.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough about me. Tell me about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:38.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you have a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:47.09,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I didn't learn much about her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:51.99,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, well. I guess I'll wait around for the old man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:56.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But will he really find him that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:02.23,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}{\fad(425,0)}One Week Later
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:04.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been to the aquarium in forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:09.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither! I hope I can pet the dolphins!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:11.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad about the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:14.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably won't rain, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:16.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The old man's working again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:23.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This Kitagawa guy moved
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:27.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}without giving his new address to the transportation office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:30.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is gonna take awhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:33.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I thought it was strange she hired a detective
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:37.51,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}when she already had his license plate number...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:39.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So that's what this really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:47.68,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:50.08,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But why does she look so sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:54.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Sorry! I just remembered I hafta do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:55.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:02.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers and mourning clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:04.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's visiting a grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.35,0:07:29.69,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I wonder whose grave it is. It still looks new.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:31.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:34.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Saeki-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:37.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to believe it's been six months already...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:38.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:41.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:44.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:47.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, all I did was help with your rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:50.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You did all the hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:54.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we have coffee somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:57.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I need to hurry home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:01.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Then let me drive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:04.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. Thanks, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:09.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:11.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:13.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:15.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose grave is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:19.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.21,0:08:24.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it was that lady's boyfriend's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:30.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is. He was both my friend and her fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:32.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her fiancé? When did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:35.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Yamaguchi Family Grave"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:35.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Early June.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:37.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}June?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:40.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No doubt about it! It was the guy in the picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:43.40,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This was my boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:46.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}until he dumped me a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:50.41,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0} lied about being dumped
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:52.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}when her boyfriend was actually dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:54.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:57.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Say, how did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:02.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The two were driving through scenic Shinshu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:04.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when they drove into a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:10.89,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Pardon my asking, but how are you two related?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:15.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I met him in early June, during a trip to Shinshu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What does it mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:23.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Did she meet him when her fiancé caused the accident?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:26.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Have you ever heard the name\NTsuyoshi Kitagawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:27.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:30.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He drives a red sports car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:32.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A red sports car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:33.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:35.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:39.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! It has to do with that lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:42.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}?! Who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:45.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Conan Edogawa. A detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:47.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:53.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:57.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that the famous Detective Mouri\Nwould have an assistant like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:10:01.68,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It was the only way to get you to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:04.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So what are you investigating?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:07.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give any details, but could you start
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:12.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by giving me the name of Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s fiancé?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:15.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His name was Tatsuo Yamaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He worked at the same company as she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:22.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, you seemed surprised when I mentioned a red sports car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:28.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard her talking to the police\Nafter the accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:31.71,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A red sports car?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:36.44,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yes. There was a young couple in it, chasing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.28,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We tried to lose them, but then—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:42.38,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We did find two sets of tire tracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:44.39,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}but why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.39,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}They were just harassing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:50.73,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}At first they kept honking their horn from behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:54.40,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and when we let them go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:57.00,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}they swerved right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:11:00.54,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Tatsuo-{\i1}san{\i0} tried to avoid them, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:01.60,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:05.41,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Alright. We're looking into the incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:09.58,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}but even if we do catch them, they'll probably get off easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:11.15,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}How come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:15.22,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Things might've been different had you actually collided,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:19.72,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}but as they are now, this would be deemed Yamaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0}'s fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:21.92,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He was speeding, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:27.86,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Do you remember the car's model\Nor license plate number?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:34.54,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Okaya-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:40.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Then she answered clearly with\N"I don't remember."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:43.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she didn't remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:46.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It was really hard on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:50.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't describe the couple very well either,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:56.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and with no other leads, the police investigation ended after only a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:59.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So those clues...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:02.76,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yes. His license plate number
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.93,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and a quick sketch of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:08.60,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh! He's quite the unique individual!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:12.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0} remembered\Nhis plate number and his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:16.18,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Does the fact that she didn't tell the police
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:19.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}mean that she's going\Nto take matters into her own hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:29.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Saeki-{\i1}san{\i0}! What was the rehabilitation you and Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0} talked about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:34.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the doctor in charge of her rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:37.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did she seem at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:41.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She worked extremely hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:47.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What normally takes half a year,\Nshe did in three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:49.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:51.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:55.53,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Her lust for revenge inspired her\Nto get better quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:59.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Saeki-{\i1}san{\i0}! Let's go see Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0} right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:00.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:01.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:07.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I have to somehow change Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:10.78,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}before the old man finds this Kitagawa guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:12.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But how—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:18.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry! That's a Shakoba Cactus needle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:21.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've gotten there when I recently
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:24.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,took one to a friend's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:29.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shakoba Cactus? Was it Yamaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0}'s?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:34.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He had raised cactuses since he was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:39.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I took all of them in after the accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:43.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but someone asked for one, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:46.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to share them with Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:50.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but that would only remind her of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:54.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So she doesn't know I have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:58.93,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait! Shakoba Cactuses are also known as Christmas Cactuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:00.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What if—!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:02.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Say, is your house far from here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:06.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's on the way to Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:07.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's stop by there first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:08.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's not home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:15.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:18.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's odd. There's no telling when the old man will contact her,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:21.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}so she should be at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:24.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Don't tell me he's already found the address?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Mouri Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:31.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:34.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find out the guy's address already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:37.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, sure did! Wasn't easy, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:39.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wore the bottoms off of my shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it? Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:45.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got off the phone with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:46.41,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:50.25,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But the guy's already living with some chick,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:52.65,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}so I guess she's out of luck—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Give me the address, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:56.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:15:00.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, before that couple gets killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:01.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:15.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}\N{\blur0\c\3c}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:28.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}katamuite-yuku hizashi ga nagai sakamichi terashite-iru\N{\blur0\c\3c}The last rays of sunlight flow down the long hill
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:40.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}kimi wa hitori de hashiru kawaita nodo osaete\N{\blur0\c\3c}You run up it alone, despite your parched throat
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:55.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}motsuresou ni naru ashimoto akirame ga mada osoikakaru\N{\blur0\c\3c}Feeling about to stumble anytime, the desire to give up floods back
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:16:07.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}yosoku dekinai happening kidou hazureta yume\N{\blur0\c\3c}Events you could never expect have thrown your dream off course
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:21.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}kokoro kowareteku itami no naka\N{\blur0\c\3c}But when your heart's falling apart from the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:34.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}wasurenaide-hoshii koko ni iru-kara\N{\blur0\c\3c}Never forget that I'm always here for you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:16.35,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Losers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:33.54,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:42.56,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Tatsuo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:57.01,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0} probably went to the transportation office
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:59.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}on her own to find Kitagawa's address.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:04.62,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Unable to find his new address, she hired the old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:07.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If she was that intent on rehabilitation,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:13.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}then there's probably no stopping her\Nfrom wanting vengeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:18.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}How is she planning to get revenge, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:20.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Say, did Yamaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0} die instantly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:25.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He was still alive after he smashed into the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:28.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He burned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Burned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:33.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The car's gasoline ignited before he could be pulled out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:39.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Aha! That wasn't kerosene at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:41.38,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It was probably gasoline!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:22.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:25.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:29.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That accident wasn't our fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:33.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your excuses; you're both going to die now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:34.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:43.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:46.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are human scum! Get ready to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:50.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to suffer exactly like my boyfriend did!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:53.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the crazy one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.73,0:19:00.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:10.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably the only way to calm her feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:26.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! What are you doin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:29.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:34.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}! Stop this foolishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:36.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:40.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing this won't bring Yamaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0} back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:44.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that! But this is all I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:49.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it! Light it on fire and you'll be injured too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:50.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:55.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no future now that Tatsuo-{\i1}san{\i0} is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:58.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The least I can do is make these people pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:12.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, I'm pooped...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:14.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:18.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This Shakoba Cactus sure is pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:21.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They bloom in the winter, so in some countries
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:23.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they're given as Christmas presents
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:26.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and even referred to as Christmas Cactuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:38.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Tatsuo-{\i1}san{\i0}'s Shakoba Cactus?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:44.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I took in all of his cactuses as mementos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:03.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:06.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0} may have died,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:10.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but he lives on in each one of these flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:26.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:17.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've come!\NThe aquarium was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.82,0:23:20.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of us fed the dolphins!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.63,0:23:24.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0} slipped and fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:29.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The aquarium guy took a picture\Nat that exact moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:30.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See!
